想着我的故事
with my homuncular image rattling in your gonads.

4
00:03:01.850 --> 00:03:03.890 
去感觉
Feel...

5
00:03:03.850 --> 00:03:06.100 
我从前的感觉 我现在的感觉
how it was for me, how it is for me.

6
00:03:05.860 --> 00:03:07.900 
去思考
And ponder.

7
