Did he know something more profound?

9
00:03:16.370 --> 00:03:19.980 
是不是有些事情
Or is there some wall of wretchedness that we all batter with our heads

10
00:03:19.870 --> 00:03:22.330 
让你觉得终生后悔？
at that shining live-long moment?

